{
  "stem": "2690.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they used to say, yes, your English is so nice and very refined.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, well, this is the way I always spoke.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- because we had to use-- we could use the-- the kitchens of the hotels.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "See, the hotels were taken for us, that we could stay somewhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was not always space for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So one was in a-- in this hotel, the other in that hotel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were not always together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my husband was with me and my daughter, but my other family were in different hotels.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we could go outside but not we were not free to walk around because they was-- always the Germans were the boss there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day, my husband, of course, he had the-- with his ear, he had to go to the hospital in Nancy, N-A-N-C-Y, Nancy.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And going there, they operated on him and he walked around there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a prison near the hospital, and one of the men that was in the hospital said, there's a Dutch woman in the prison.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was, down below-- and my husband walked by and said, in Dutch, are you Dutch?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Are you Dutch?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he found the woman and--",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
